---
// No AnimatedSection — CTA should be immediately visible
---

<section
  class="px-6 md:px-16 py-section border-t border-ink bg-ink text-canvas"
  aria-labelledby="seminar-cta-heading"
>
  <p class="text-xs font-bold tracking-[0.2em] uppercase opacity-40 mb-6">
    Train with Alvin
  </p>

  <h2
    id="seminar-cta-heading"
    class="text-5xl md:text-7xl lg:text-8xl font-black tracking-[-0.04em] leading-[1.05] mb-8 max-w-4xl"
  >
    Book a Seminar
  </h2>

  <p class="text-lg md:text-xl leading-relaxed opacity-60 max-w-2xl mb-12">
    Whether you're an individual looking for private instruction, a group
    seeking structured training, or an organization planning a martial arts
    workshop — Alvin offers sessions tailored to your goals.
  </p>

  <ul
    class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 mb-16 border-t border-canvas border-opacity-20 pt-12"
  >
    <li>
      <p class="text-xl font-black tracking-[-0.04em] leading-[1.05] mb-2">
        Private Lessons
      </p>
      <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed opacity-60">
        One-on-one instruction focused on your pace, your goals, and your
        specific areas of development.
      </p>
    </li>
    <li>
      <p class="text-xl font-black tracking-[-0.04em] leading-[1.05] mb-2">
        Group Seminars
      </p>
      <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed opacity-60">
        Structured sessions for small groups covering Lapunti fundamentals,
        technique, and application.
      </p>
    </li>
    <li>
      <p class="text-xl font-black tracking-[-0.04em] leading-[1.05] mb-2">
        Organizational Workshops
      </p>
      <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed opacity-60">
        Custom workshops for schools, clubs, and organizations — from
        introductory demonstrations to multi-day intensives.
      </p>
    </li>
  </ul>

  <a
    href="/contact"
    class="inline-block bg-canvas text-ink font-black text-sm tracking-[0.15em] uppercase px-10 py-4 transition-opacity duration-200 hover:opacity-80 focus-visible:outline focus-visible:outline-offset-2 focus-visible:outline-canvas"
    aria-label="Get in touch to book a seminar or training session"
  >
    Get in Touch
  </a>
</section>
